    "name": "BEYBLADE X XONE",
    "steam_appid": 3023070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience action-packed Beyblade battles in a stadium equipped with BEYBLADE X's signature X-celerator Rail as you unleash the Xtreme Dash and use the game's original &quot;Active Gauge&quot; to execute exciting tactical maneuvers! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■STORY</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely new story featuring original game characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023070/extras/264d97206b6779aa5a4e18cfed0c306b.avif?t=1768443583\" width=500 height=141 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new tournament, the X Tower Championship, is being held at the X Tower. Compete with rivals, deepen bonds, and aim for the top of the X Tower! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■BATTLE</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Completely recreates the ultra-accelerated battles of BEYBLADE X! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the impact of extreme acceleration in a stadium equipped with the X-celerator Rail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023070/extras/eda1a84554ccde5992a9a9931caaea51.avif?t=1768443583\" width=500 height=140 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you &quot;Let it rip!&quot;, the &quot;Active Gauge&quot; fills over time. Use it to unleash critical &quot;Attacks&quot; and &quot;Counters&quot; one after another!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023070/extras/321c01657a328a058a5f1c9170b51e33.avif?t=1768443583\" width=500 height=140 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleashing critical attacks increases the X Gauge! When it reaches MAX, choose the skill you want to activate. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skills operate on a rock-paper-scissors system. Choose a skill that gives you an advantage over your opponent!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023070/extras/8211597b7a0282c20f8a1eae78258fdf.avif?t=1768443583\" width=500 height=140 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you win, activate the skill and knock your opponent out in spectacular fashion! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■CUSTOMIZE</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customization takes X Skills into account and offers over 100 million possible combinations!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely combine parts and skills to set up your Beyblade just the way you want. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023070/extras/3f489bb9a6bcd764b8a8f0a5ea33217f.avif?t=1768443583\" width=500 height=140 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ONLINE BATTLES</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In online battles, you can compete against Bladers from all corners of the globe anytime, anywhere! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge Bladers from around the world and aim for the top. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023070/extras/22c544ef530edc0e1cb48b1ef688b028.avif?t=1768443583\" width=500 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The ranking specifications may differ slightly from other platforms.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■DOWNLOADABLE CONTENT</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional Beyblades will be gradually released as downloadable content!<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >©Homura Kawamoto, Hikaru Muno, Posuka Demizu, BBXProject, TV TOKYO </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >© ＴＯＭＹ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >© FURYU Corporation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*All images are from an in-development version of the game. Content and specifications may differ in the final product.</p>",
